title: Grateful Dead - All the Years Combine - BONUS DISC
description:
All the Years Combine - BONUS DISC

An interview with music and video archivist David Lemieux, previously unreleased.

Backstage pass

Songs from five live performances, previously unreleased.

The previously unreleased songs are:

    China Cat Sunflower - October 2, 1987, Shoreline Amphitheatre, Mountain View
    I Know You Rider - October 2, 1987, Shoreline Amphitheatre, Mountain View
    Man Smart, Woman Smarter - October 2, 1987, Shoreline Amphitheatre, Mountain View
    Friend Of The Devil - July 2, 1989, Sullivan Stadium, Foxboro
    Hey Pocky Way - July 22, 1990, The World Amphitheatre, Tinley Park
    Shakedown Street - June 22, 1991, Soldier Field, Chicago
